{"tid":1905131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連環縱火】貪圖快感連環燒3港鐵站垃圾桶　51歲男涉縱火被捕","createTime":"2020-03-01T05:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T05:35:14.000Z","uid":14454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56690408f813d4132fe66e994d1ed0ae00cf4a62","tid":1905131,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"上月26日晚上發生連環縱火案，港鐵觀塘線3個車站內外垃圾桶遭焚毀，原因只為一男子貪一時之快感。警方昨日（29日）拘捕一名51歲報稱無業男子，指他當日晚上連環作案，先後於黃大仙港鐵站內外、九龍灣站及彩虹站以打火機燃點垃圾桶內紙張縱火，男子被捕後承認貪圖一時快感而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/441728/連環縱火-貪圖快感連環燒3港鐵站垃圾桶-51歲男涉縱火被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F441728%2F%E9%80%A3%E7%92%B0%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E8%B2%AA%E5%9C%96%E5%BF%AB%E6%84%9F%E9%80%A3%E7%92%B0%E7%87%923%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%A1%B6-51%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%B6%89%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGotqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=2f54c0a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/441728/連環縱火-貪圖快感連環燒3港鐵站垃圾桶-51歲男涉縱火被捕</a>"},{"pid":"4e789fc9bb409e643965487f7f6d5efd4ccc11a2","tid":1905131,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:17:38.000Z","msg":"銀髮族手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec52414467de1c575f5d8b5af2c0ff7c3185c8a0","tid":1905131,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8098c6ddf1617650c1adac6d6ac0a4bab9d1fc45","tid":1905131,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"51老破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d03e60063ec4e4ec65a5288c67c6004b5f4163","tid":1905131,"uid":198216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T05:35:14.000Z","msg":"51歲 （縱火）"}]}